    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Organized at least one training in a year to NGOs staff, volunteers, farmers and SCGs and SCO members on planning, implementing, monitoring, advocacy, gender equity and other relevant subjects as appropriate to build their local capacity.\r\n\tOrganized programme reflection and learning meeting twice a year so that partners can learn innovative approaches from each other and apply in their program areas to make their programs cost effective and maximize the benefits to more people.\r\n\tProvided training to partner NGOs on financial management, account keeping, and office management to ensure transparency, accountability, cost effectiveness of the programme.\r\n\tOrganized workshops/seminars and training to increase participants’ skill on proposal writing for fund raising, documentation and report writing.\r\n\tEstablished an alliance of peer agencies that have similar mission and purpose to WN to facilitate learning from each other in the programme areas."
      },
